EmailTemplate.textOnly: - - - Clean Clean false false false EN-US X-NONE X-NONE Hi Patrick, Great, glad to hear that. If you want to put a collateral in front of them you can use this <http://info.mbopartners.com/rs/mbo/images/MBO_Partners_Introduction.pdf>. Additionally, I would encourage you to visit and book mark my private landing page <http://info.mbopartners.com/advisor-info-s-conde.html>. There is lots of great information on here and it is always been updated and kept current. Please let me know if you have any additional questions. Good luck in your search!
